Class-DBI-Plugin-DeepAbstractSearch version 0.05
================================================

Abstract Class::DBI's SQL with SQL::Abstract, with automatically created
join queries for has_a relationships.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Class::DBI
  Class::DBI::Plugin
  SQL::Abstract

